commit.message:
re PR go/55201 (libgo.so: undefined reference to `__atomic_compare_exchange_8')

	PR go/55201
	* Makefile.am (noinst_LTLIBRARIES): Define new make variable.
	(libatomic_convenience_la_SOURCES): Likewise.
	(libatomic_convenience_la_LIBADD): Likewise.
	* Makefile.in: Rebuild.
	* testsuite/Makefile.in: Rebuild.

From-SVN: r194592

files.patch:
@@ -1,3 +1,12 @@
+2012-12-18  Ian Lance Taylor  <iant@google.com>
+
+	PR go/55201
+	* Makefile.am (noinst_LTLIBRARIES): Define new make variable.
+	(libatomic_convenience_la_SOURCES): Likewise.
+	(libatomic_convenience_la_LIBADD): Likewise.
+	* Makefile.in: Rebuild.
+	* testsuite/Makefile.in: Rebuild.
+
 2012-12-04  Marcus Shawcroft  <marcus.shawcroft@arm.com>
 
 	* config/arm/arm-config.h (__ARM_ARCH_8A__): New.

@@ -40,6 +40,7 @@ AM_CCASFLAGS = $(XCFLAGS)
 AM_LDFLAGS = $(XLDFLAGS) $(SECTION_LDFLAGS) $(OPT_LDFLAGS)
 
 toolexeclib_LTLIBRARIES = libatomic.la
+noinst_LTLIBRARIES = libatomic_convenience.la
 
 if LIBAT_BUILD_VERSIONED_SHLIB
 if LIBAT_BUILD_VERSIONED_SHLIB_GNU

 endif
 endif
+
+libatomic_convenience_la_SOURCES = $(libatomic_la_SOURCES)
+libatomic_convenience_la_LIBADD = $(libatomic_la_LIBADD)

   sed '$$!N;$$!N;$$!N;$$!N;$$!N;$$!N;$$!N;s/\n/ /g' | \

-LTLIBRARIES = $(toolexeclib_LTLIBRARIES)
+LTLIBRARIES = $(noinst_LTLIBRARIES) $(toolexeclib_LTLIBRARIES)

 	glfree.lo lock.lo init.lo
 libatomic_la_OBJECTS = $(am_libatomic_la_OBJECTS)

 	$(LIBTOOLFLAGS) --mode=link $(CCLD) $(AM_CFLAGS) $(CFLAGS) \
 	$(libatomic_la_LDFLAGS) $(LDFLAGS) -o $@
+libatomic_convenience_la_DEPENDENCIES = $(libatomic_la_LIBADD)
+am__objects_1 = gload.lo gstore.lo gcas.lo gexch.lo glfree.lo lock.lo \
+	init.lo
+am_libatomic_convenience_la_OBJECTS = $(am__objects_1)
+libatomic_convenience_la_OBJECTS =  \
+	$(am_libatomic_convenience_la_OBJECTS)

@@ -107,7 +113,8 @@ CCLD = $(CC)
 LINK = $(LIBTOOL) --tag=CC $(AM_LIBTOOLFLAGS) $(LIBTOOLFLAGS) \
 	--mode=link $(CCLD) $(AM_CFLAGS) $(CFLAGS) $(AM_LDFLAGS) \
 	$(LDFLAGS) -o $@
-SOURCES = $(libatomic_la_SOURCES) $(EXTRA_libatomic_la_SOURCES)
+SOURCES = $(libatomic_la_SOURCES) $(EXTRA_libatomic_la_SOURCES) \
+	$(libatomic_convenience_la_SOURCES)
 MULTISRCTOP = 
 MULTIBUILDTOP = 
 MULTIDIRS = 
@@ -270,6 +277,7 @@ AM_CFLAGS = $(XCFLAGS)
 AM_CCASFLAGS = $(XCFLAGS)

 toolexeclib_LTLIBRARIES = libatomic.la

 @LIBAT_BUILD_VERSIONED_SHLIB_FALSE@libatomic_version_script = 
 @LIBAT_BUILD_VERSIONED_SHLIB_GNU_TRUE@@LIBAT_BUILD_VERSIONED_SHLIB_TRUE@libatomic_version_script = -Wl,--version-script,$(top_srcdir)/libatomic.map
 @LIBAT_BUILD_VERSIONED_SHLIB_SUN_TRUE@@LIBAT_BUILD_VERSIONED_SHLIB_TRUE@libatomic_version_script = -Wl,-M,libatomic.map-sun
@@ -308,6 +316,8 @@ libatomic_la_LIBADD = $(foreach s,$(SIZES),$(addsuffix \
 @ARCH_ARM_LINUX_TRUE@@HAVE_IFUNC_TRUE@IFUNC_OPTIONS = -march=armv7-a -DHAVE_KERNEL64

+libatomic_convenience_la_LIBADD = $(libatomic_la_LIBADD)
 all: auto-config.h
 	$(MAKE) $(AM_MAKEFLAGS) all-recursive
 
@@ -364,6 +374,15 @@ $(srcdir)/auto-config.h.in: @MAINTAINER_MODE_TRUE@ $(am__configure_deps)
 
 distclean-hdr:
 	-rm -f auto-config.h stamp-h1
+
+clean-noinstLTLIBRARIES:
+	-test -z "$(noinst_LTLIBRARIES)" || rm -f $(noinst_LTLIBRARIES)
+	@list='$(noinst_LTLIBRARIES)'; for p in $$list; do \
+	  dir="`echo $$p | sed -e 's|/[^/]*$$||'`"; \
+	  test "$$dir" != "$$p" || dir=.; \
+	  echo "rm -f \"$${dir}/so_locations\""; \
+	  rm -f "$${dir}/so_locations"; \
+	done
 install-toolexeclibLTLIBRARIES: $(toolexeclib_LTLIBRARIES)
 	@$(NORMAL_INSTALL)
 	test -z "$(toolexeclibdir)" || $(MKDIR_P) "$(DESTDIR)$(toolexeclibdir)"
@@ -397,6 +416,8 @@ clean-toolexeclibLTLIBRARIES:
 	done
 libatomic.la: $(libatomic_la_OBJECTS) $(libatomic_la_DEPENDENCIES) 
 	$(libatomic_la_LINK) -rpath $(toolexeclibdir) $(libatomic_la_OBJECTS) $(libatomic_la_LIBADD) $(LIBS)
+libatomic_convenience.la: $(libatomic_convenience_la_OBJECTS) $(libatomic_convenience_la_DEPENDENCIES) 
+	$(LINK)  $(libatomic_convenience_la_OBJECTS) $(libatomic_convenience_la_LIBADD) $(LIBS)

 	-rm -f *.$(OBJEXT)
@@ -628,8 +649,8 @@ maintainer-clean-generic:
 	@echo "it deletes files that may require special tools to rebuild."

-clean-am: clean-generic clean-libtool clean-toolexeclibLTLIBRARIES \
-	mostlyclean-am

+	clean-toolexeclibLTLIBRARIES mostlyclean-am

+	clean-noinstLTLIBRARIES clean-toolexeclibLTLIBRARIES ctags \
+	ctags-recursive distclean distclean-compile distclean-generic \
+	distclean-hdr distclean-libtool distclean-multi distclean-tags \
+	dvi dvi-am html html-am info info-am install install-am \
+	install-data install-data-am install-dvi install-dvi-am \
+	install-exec install-exec-am install-html install-html-am \
+	install-info install-info-am install-man install-multi \
+	install-pdf install-pdf-am install-ps install-ps-am \
+	install-strip install-toolexeclibLTLIBRARIES installcheck \
+	installcheck-am installdirs installdirs-am maintainer-clean \
 	maintainer-clean-generic maintainer-clean-multi mostlyclean \
 	mostlyclean-compile mostlyclean-generic mostlyclean-libtool \
 	mostlyclean-multi pdf pdf-am ps ps-am tags tags-recursive \
